examples.text: İhya Bey o değil abi. Na şu gelen. Her önüne çıkan uyuzla konuşmasana.
examples.translation: That's not İhya Bey, my brother. İhya Bey is this fellow coming this way. Why do you talk to any old scab that you meet around the corner?

etymology: From Russian на (na) or Ukrainian на (na). Doublet of nah.
